{"word":"H3554 - כָּוָה - kâvâh - kaw-vaw' - Burn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּוָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâvâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-vaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Burn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுடு, வேகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to burn, to scorch, to brand; (Niphal) to be burned, to be scorched"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>prick</i> or <i>penetrate</i>; hence to <i>blister</i> (as smarting or eating into): - burn."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3554 - כָּוָה - kâvâh - kaw-vaw'/3554\">H3554</a>, <a href=\"#/H3555 - כְּוִיָּה - kᵉvîyâh - kev-ee-yaw'/3555\">H3555</a>, <a href=\"#/H3587 - כִּי - kîy - kee/3587\">H3587</a>, <a href=\"#/H4348 - מִכְוָה - mikvâh - mik-vaw'/4348\">H4348</a>"}]}